{"tid":2326788,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel 宣佈《Guardians of the Galaxy》「星爵 Star-Lord」為雙性戀角色","createTime":"2020-12-15T14:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T11:47:57.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"82da0cbc8f7943dfd52924c97af92276ff5db0ae","tid":2326788,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T14:30:42.000Z","msg":"漫畫《Guardians of the Galaxy》第 9 集中透露了「星爵 Star-Lord」Peter Quill 的更多性向情報。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在過去 Peter Quill 因逃亡意外抵達 Morinus 星球，便遇到了兩位有著淺綠色外觀的外星人 Aradia 和 Mors（一男一女），兩人向 Peter 展示了自身種族對性向的開放性，不過在當時 Peter 仍希望趕緊回到女友 Gamora 的身邊，對此深信不宜。12 年後，Peter Quill 終於坦然接受這份關係，漫畫中三人進行共浴，其中男性角色甚至說道：「You&rsquo;re newborn and ready to learn our way.」而此關係似乎正式確立 Peter Quill 為雙性戀角色，成為 Marvel 最新 LGBT 家族一員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有趣的是 Chris Pratt 在現實生活中為虔誠基督教徒，此設定是否將在未來加入 MCU 中，有待日後官方確認。"},{"pid":"d61c6644a8a22c30de1df258212f354cd57014f7","tid":2326788,"uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":39,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T14:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tGbzE9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tGbzE9.jpg&h=a329e2da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b32504e8d6e32ae0e4a8eb68103fad3ee159a9ce","tid":2326788,"uid":76804,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"曬黑埋做黑人呀唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33154fe4b8389694950f06ae8ac57566379480b","tid":2326788,"uid":41974,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T14:33:04.000Z","msg":"電影呢個Chris 係冇表態支持支那登嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f2fd20a2baf1fe5c0c6b1da48247eb41324efb","tid":2326788,"uid":18479,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T14:33:26.000Z","msg":"雙性戀咁少 marvel已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src